tasks.details:
Build UI components and settings management interface for workspace-specific participant preferences. The API infrastructure and database schema are already in place with the preferences JSONB field added to WorkspaceMembership.

Remaining implementation focuses on:

1. **Settings UI Components**: Create comprehensive settings interface using shadcn/ui with form sections for each preference category:
   - Notification settings (frequency, types, quiet hours)
   - Privacy controls (leaderboard opt-in, profile visibility, DM permissions)
   - Participation preferences (landing view, interests, reminders)
   - Time/locale settings (timezone, week start, time format)
   - Data controls (export permissions, leave workspace)

2. **Settings Management Interface**: Build workspace-specific settings page at `/w/[slug]/settings/preferences` with:
   - Form validation and error handling
   - Save/cancel functionality with optimistic updates
   - Real-time preference updates
   - Integration with existing workspace navigation

3. **Enhanced Profile Integration**: Connect preference settings with enhanced profile components:
   - Display preference-based customizations in profile views
   - Respect privacy settings in participant listings
   - Apply notification preferences to system communications
   - Honor time/locale preferences in UI formatting

TypeScript interfaces for preference structure:
```typescript
interface ParticipantPreferences {
  notifications: {
    frequency: 'real-time' | 'hourly' | 'daily';
    types: {
      challengePublished: boolean;
      enrollmentChanges: boolean;
      activityReminders: boolean;
      reviewOutcomes: boolean;
      pointsChanges: boolean;
    };
    quietHours: {
      enabled: boolean;
      startTime: string; // HH:MM format
      endTime: string;
    };
  };
  privacy: {
    leaderboardOptIn: boolean;
    profileVisibility: 'public' | 'workspace' | 'private';
    dmPermissions: 'all' | 'admins-only' | 'none';
  };
  participation: {
    defaultLandingView: 'dashboard' | 'challenges' | 'leaderboard';
    challengeInterests: string[];
    reminderCadence: 'daily' | 'weekly' | 'never';
  };
  timeAndLocale: {
    timezoneOverride?: string;
    weekStart: 'sunday' | 'monday';
    timeFormat: '12h' | '24h';
  };
  dataControls: {
    allowDataExport: boolean;
    allowLeaveWorkspace: boolean;
  };
}
```
